{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_enabled_selected_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_enabled_selected_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Inverse","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Inverse"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_enabled_selected_OrangeInverse","type":"image"